						 <p>A solid conclusion to a solid entry for the Doomsday Contest.</p> <p>I particularly like the reaffirmation throughout the tale that the narrator is a good man, only for it to be missing at the end. In my opinion that is what gives this tale a final punch that is quite powerful.</p> <p>+1.</p> 
