						 <p>I thought I was done with doomcon when I wrote Paperpushing. I came to the realization while I was taking cosplay pictures with the car the other day that no, I was not done. Now I am. See you on the other side, civilians. Could this be the end?<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-737629-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup></p> <p>Thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530396679" alt="WrongJohnSilver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" >WrongJohnSilver</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530396679" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" >Rimple</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sly161" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2969980&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530396679" alt="Sly161" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2969980)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sly161" >Sly161</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2812984&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530396679" alt="AbsentmindedNihilist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2812984)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" >AbsentmindedNihilist</a></span> for draft feedback.</p>